{
  "stem": "3360.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But the democratic government, that [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Weinmar, ?] the democracy, was not working very well because the Germans were too deep in debt to the Allies, who had won the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they just couldn't get out from under, and it got-- it went from bad to worse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well anyway, that's how, of course, Hitler got some of his foothold, because of the-- one of the reasons, at least-- because of the desperate economic situation.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we would talk about an upcoming election, and we were really quite into what was going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was Hindenburg, he was the old general.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was the Nazi party, and there were the Social Democrats-- that was a big party-- and there was a Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was another party, which was the Catholic party.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So those were the big parties, and we would talk about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember very distinctly one of my friends saying, well, you know, my-- well, I think my parents-- one would say, well, my parents will probably vote for Hitler because he has the best program, and for what they could tell at that point.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And another one would say, my parents don't trust Hitler at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think they're going to vote for him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So those are the kinds of conversations we had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very innocent, it, it, it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And another thing that I remember about my walk to and from school in the morning--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CLEARING THROAT] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I had quite a walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for, for lunch-- we didn't have regular lunch periods, like we do here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First of all, we weren't in school that long, but it was a more, it was a more concentrated session, the hours that we did spend there.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
